PrecisReappointment of GENEVIÈVE BOUDREAU of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Parole Board of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of five years; and her designation as full-time member and Vice-Chairperson of the Appeal Division of the Parole Board of Canada, effective March 26, 2023.
